<div class="title">Am So Glad I Found You</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=trip2live&Exact=1">trip2live</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; trip2live. "Am So Glad I Found You: An Experience with 2C-I & Cannabis (exp38472)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 25, 2005. erowid.org/exp/38472</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
